com.cerner.bunsen.spark.codes

Class Ancestor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.bunsen.spark.codes.Ancestor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Ancestor
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A JavaBean to represent a ancestor row from one value to another. This class is mutable for easy use as a Spark Dataset<Ancestor> instance.
